column8: Widespread embedded black algae, indicative of failing anti-fouling properties
May need new prop anode on next service. Removed wrapped line or kelp wrapped around prop, see video. Paint required extra scrubbing to remove growth.
Replaced Autostream prop anode.  I’m ordering a second for your spares inventory, this will be added to this month’s bill.
Widespread embedded algae. Propspeed mostly worn away. A haulout is recommended.
Paint has become ineffective. Haul out recommended asap.
Will probably need prop anode on next service
Prospered is gone. Will return with anodes (2) shaft, R2, Autostream
